$Id$

Planned features:

Version 1.0:
* cc/sl: zooming control on toolbar
* sl: on/off rectangle update
* sl: block "garbage" effect when rectangle is outside screen
* sl: Add "Pause" button to pause to the current view
- sl: Grab window moving with the mouse
- sl: Allow setting of refresh rate
- sl: Add grabbing and saving of the currently selected area or zoomed area.
- sl: Saving of settings across different instances
- sl: Add printing support
- sl: Code cleanup
-   : Translations
-   : New Icon

Bug Fixing for 1.0:
- sl: When the zoom area is resized, the zoom display shows garbage outside
      the zoomed region
- sl: Sometimes the zoom area window remains on the screen


Version 2.0:
- cc: zoom rectangle moving from spinboxes
- cc: on/off zoom rectangle
- cc: block mirrror-to-mirror efect when zoom rectangle intersect KMag window
- cc: configuration dialog
- sl: Add option to show the region-selection window all the time.
-     Different profiles : for vision-impared & regular users.

